<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Maomaomoka</title>
<style>
:root {
    --bg-light: #fffaf6;
    --bg-dark: #1e1e2f;
    --text-light: #2c2c2c;
    --text-dark: #f0f0f5;
    --accent: #7c3aed;
    --accent-dark: #9d7aff;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
    background: var(--bg-light);
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    transition: background 0.4s, color 0.4s;
}

body.dark-mode {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    color: var(--text-dark);
}

header {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

header p {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #f0e6ff;
}

header .motto {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #f0e6ff;
    font-size: 1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1.5s forwards 0.5s;
}

nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: #5b21b6;
}

nav a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 15px 25px;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: background 0.3s;
}

nav a:hover {
    background-color: #4b1da0;
}

section {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 50px 20px;
}

section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: var(--accent);
}

.about-me img {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid var(--accent);
    object-fit: cover;
}

.about-me p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: auto;
}

.writing-section {
    background: #f0ebff;
    padding: 25px 30px;
    border-left: 5px solid var(--accent);
    margin: 20px 0;
    min-height: 120px;
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s forwards;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    cursor: default;
}

body.dark-mode .writing-section {
    background: #2e2e44;
}

.writing-section:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 15px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    resize: vertical;
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
}

button {
    background-color: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-right: 10px;
    transition: background 0.3s;
}

button:hover {
    background-color: #5b21b6;
}

.mode-toggle {
    position: fixed;
    top: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    background-color: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    transition: background 0.3s;
}

.mode-toggle:hover {
    background-color: #5b21b6;
}

a.email-link {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
}

a.email-link:hover {
    color: #5b21b6;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<button class="mode-toggle" onclick="toggleMode()">Toggle Dark/Light Mode</button>

<header>
    <h1>Maomaomoka</h1>
    <p>"A little corner to think, write, and wander inside my head."</p>
    <p class="motto">"Don’t ever take your back kind hand."</p>
</header>

<nav>
    <a href="#about">About Me</a>
    <a href="#writing">My Writings</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section id="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <div class="about-me">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/180" alt="Maomaomoka's Portrait">
        <p>
            Hey, I’m Maomaomoka. I like quiet corners, fleeting thoughts, and the small moments  
            that make life feel a little magical. Sometimes I write, sometimes I just observe.  
            This is my corner, where words linger and sometimes even dance.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="writing">
    <h2>My Writings</h2>
    <div id="posts">
        <div class="writing-section">
            <p><em>Welcome! This is my little space for thoughts, sketches of ideas, or even random musings. Go ahead, add something!</em></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <textarea id="newPost" rows="4" placeholder="Write something here..."></textarea>
    <button onclick="addPost()">Add to My Corner</button>
</section>

<section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p style="text-align:center;">
        If my reflections resonate, or you just want to say hi,  
        drop me a note at <a class="email-link" href="mailto:maomaomoka@example.com">maomaomoka@example.com</a>.
    </p>
</section>

<footer>
    &copy; 2026 Maomaomoka. All reflections reserved.
</footer>

<script>
function addPost() {
    const textArea = document.getElementById('newPost');
    const postText = textArea.value.trim();
    if(postText === '') return;

    const postsDiv = document.getElementById('posts');
    const newPost = document.createElement('div');
    newPost.className = 'writing-section';
    newPost.innerHTML = `<p>${postText}</p>`;
    postsDiv.prepend(newPost);
    textArea.value = '';
}

function toggleMode() {
    document.body.classList.toggle('dark-mode');
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
